reviewText: Pretty good lil show. Mostly it's fab! The only thing is... in one episode the mom made a strawberry lentil cake. That's just nasty,  ain't nobody got time for that!  Minus one star.
My son loves all of it.

I remember this show from childhood and it was great to share it with my young family. I have to say some of the context seemed a little mature for the target group, but like most media I assume this is for adult entertainment.
What an awesome surprise to see one of my favorite old shows.  And to be able to stream it for free was just another bonus!
I remember watching Bobby's World years ago. I introduced it to my children recently. They share my passion for this great show! It  was one of the greatest cartoons ever!
I have always loved this show!
Absolutely love Bobbys world. And so does my 5year old
I remember Bobby's world as a kid it was my favorite so do buy! <3
My kids 9 and 6 love it just like I did! Funny and cute!
Classic and timeless comedy.  Me and my 8 year old love watching this show together
